e → identifier<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; attribute-argument-clause → ( balanced-tokens&lt;sub&gt;opt&lt;opt&gt; )<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; balanced-tokens → balanced-token<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; balanced-tokens → balanced-token, balanced-tokens<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; balanced-token → attribute-argument-label : attribute argument-value<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; This design can be summarized as &quot;wherever current Swift attributes use =, use : instead&quot;.<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; <br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Alternatives Considered<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; <br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; There are no alternatives to put forth other than not accepting this proposal.<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; _______________________________________________<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; swift-evolution mailing list<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; swift-evolution at swift.org<br>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; https://lists.swift.org/mailman/listinfo/swift-evolution<br>&gt;&gt;&gt; <br>&gt;&gt;&gt; _______________________________________________<br>&gt;&gt;&gt; swift-evolution mailing list<br>&gt;&gt;&gt; swift-evolution at swift.org<br>&gt;&gt;&gt; https://lists.swift.org/mailman/listinfo/swift-evolution<br>&gt; <br>&gt; _______________________________________________<br>&gt; swift-evolution mailing list<br>&gt; swift-evolution at swift.org<br>&gt; https://lists.swift.org/mailman/listinfo/swift-evolution<br>-------------- next part --------------<br>An HTML attachment was scrubbed...<br>URL: &lt;https://lists.swift.org/pipermail/swift-evolution/attachments/20160217/1386d7d6/attachment.html&gt;<br></p></div><ul class="comments"><li class="comment"><div class="avatar"><img src="https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/c40db4457ab2c91a0d8006da31b177c6?s=50"></div><header><strong>[Discussion] Replacing Equal Signs with Colons For Attribute Arguments</strong> from <string>Trent Nadeau</string> &lt;tanadeau at gmail.com&gt;<p>February 17, 2016 at 01:00:00pm</p></header><div class="content"><p>+1 from me as well<br></p><p>On Wed, Feb 17, 2